    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>HOW TO PLAY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is designed to help you expand your vocabulary in your chosen language. Here’s how it works:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play Crossword Puzzles</strong> – Each puzzle presents clues in your native language, and your task is to fill in the correct word in the foreign language</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Review &amp; Track Progress</strong> – Visit the review section to revisit all the words you've encountered</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A <strong>thumbs up</strong> means you correctly remembered the word</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A <strong>thumbs down</strong> means you got it wrong</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Words you struggle with will appear more often, while familiar words will appear less frequently</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Get Help When Needed</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you are a complete beginner the <strong>hat</strong> or <strong>book</strong> icon will help you with words you haven't encountered before, until you build up your vocabulary and hints start appearing less frequently</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Or if you already have some knowledge in the language you can use the<strong> hints</strong> on the side to help you when you are stuck</p></li></ul></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep playing, reviewing, and improving your vocabulary step by step</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SUPPORTED LANGUAGES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220820/extras/c9eb93290b04aafdc6dd18ba6aa8f415.poster.avif?t=1741619595\" width=800 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220820/extras/c9eb93290b04aafdc6dd18ba6aa8f415.webm?t=1741619595\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220820/extras/c9eb93290b04aafdc6dd18ba6aa8f415.mp4?t=1741619595\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>| ENGLISH | FRENCH | SPANISH | BULGARIAN | UKRAINIAN | TURKISH | ROMANIAN | RUSSIAN | PORTUGUESE | GERMAN |</strong> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SOLVE CROSSWORDS</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220820/extras/48b38bf04afd5c21cac445120249bddc.poster.avif?t=1741619595\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220820/extras/48b38bf04afd5c21cac445120249bddc.webm?t=1741619595\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220820/extras/48b38bf04afd5c21cac445120249bddc.mp4?t=1741619595\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Progressive word difficulty from level A1 to level C2 </strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> Ability to upload your own word lists</strong> </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>REVIEW OLD WORDS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220820/extras/932cd87d9ce72ab815fc46ee38cb9739.poster.avif?t=1741619595\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220820/extras/932cd87d9ce72ab815fc46ee38cb9739.webm?t=1741619595\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220820/extras/932cd87d9ce72ab815fc46ee38cb9739.mp4?t=1741619595\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Review words with spaced repetition</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>THIS IS NOT A TEST...</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>REVEAL A RANDOM LETTER</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220820/extras/84f5278808b1e69bb5315b3d8b1b05d0.poster.avif?t=1741619595\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220820/extras/84f5278808b1e69bb5315b3d8b1b05d0.webm?t=1741619595\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220820/extras/84f5278808b1e69bb5315b3d8b1b05d0.mp4?t=1741619595\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>REVEAL A CHOSEN LETTER</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220820/extras/cb1886f5245a438e0365c833085422d7.poster.avif?t=1741619595\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220820/extras/cb1886f5245a438e0365c833085422d7.webm?t=1741619595\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220820/extras/cb1886f5245a438e0365c833085422d7.mp4?t=1741619595\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>REVEAL A RANDOM WORD</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220820/extras/c3c9e2ca90162774e4c62a0dd2f6b20b.poster.avif?t=1741619595\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220820/extras/c3c9e2ca90162774e4c62a0dd2f6b20b.webm?t=1741619595\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220820/extras/c3c9e2ca90162774e4c62a0dd2f6b20b.mp4?t=1741619595\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Never get stuck...</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>LEARN A LANGUAGE FROM SCRATCH</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ABSOLUTE BEGINNER MODE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220820/extras/1a9ecbb0d58caeca9e5a81b86da3cea3.poster.avif?t=1741619595\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220820/extras/1a9ecbb0d58caeca9e5a81b86da3cea3.webm?t=1741619595\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220820/extras/1a9ecbb0d58caeca9e5a81b86da3cea3.mp4?t=1741619595\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BEGINNER MODE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220820/extras/9150484a095c55ec17938348de92182e.poster.avif?t=1741619595\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220820/extras/9150484a095c55ec17938348de92182e.webm?t=1741619595\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220820/extras/9150484a095c55ec17938348de92182e.mp4?t=1741619595\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>How can you solve crosswords if you know 0 words? With these two beginner modes, you will get help with words that you see for the first time</strong></p>",
